spec_data.Name: gists
spec_data.Description:
CLI interface for managing GitHub Gists.
Use it:
* List of Gists
* Show a Gist
* Download a Gist
* Create a Gist
* Update a Gist
* Fork a Gist
* Star a Gist
* Unstar a Gist
